Interface Getter<E,T>

  • Type Parameters:
    E - The class for which the getter is to be invoked
    T - The class of values returned by the call to get()
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FieldGetter, MethodGetter

    public interface Getter<E,T>
    The Getter interface defines a generic interface for getting values from a field or getter method.
